Valkuil servers

The timbl spellmods run on four machines; the WOPR servers run on two
machines. To start up:

on bythos|chronos|sphinx|phoenix:/exp/antalb/valkuil/valkuil-servers

% timblserver --config=confusibles.conf &

on bythos|phoenix:/exp/antalb/valkuil/valkuil-servers

% wopr -r server_sc -p ibasefile:ValkuilCorpus.1.1.tok.1Mlines.txt.l3r3_-a1+D.ibase,timbl:"-a1 +D",lexicon:ValkuilCorpus.1.1.tok.1Mlines.txt.lex,port:2001,keep:1,mwl:5,max_distr:250,min_ratio:100 &

timblserver runs on port 2000; wopr runs on port 2001.
